OL,5, All victims who are tricked into       
OL,6, sending money to scammers should be    
OL,7, refunded by their banks, a consumer    
OL,8, group has said.                        
OL,10,FWhich? said victims face a "lottery"   
OL,11,Fwhen it comes to getting their money   
OL,12,Fback.                                  
OL,14,FAt the moment, a voluntary code means  
OL,15,Fsome victims are compensated, but      
OL,16,Fothers are not.                        
OL,18,FThe UK's payments watchdog wants to    
OL,19,Fmake compensation mandatory and the    
OL,20,Fgovernment announced a plan a year ago.
